      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING DALILA (4) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (35.07) at this track. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Can discover winning form. MAGIC SCOTCH (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (35.04) in a R/A FIN at this track. Form here sound including two wins. Deserves plenty of respect. HE SHINES (1) produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at Traralgon over 570m behind Motor City Rossi (33.59) in a Grade 5. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. BLACK THUMB (8) is worth consideration after filling a hole at this course and distance last start.",
